## Step 5 — Initialize Git and Push

Run these commands **one by one**:

```bash
# Initialize git in your project folder
git init

# Connect to your GitHub repo
git remote add origin https://github.com/rcrahul0001-web/online-retail-dashboard.git

# Stage all files
git add .

# Check what's being added (optional but recommended)
git status

# Commit with a message
git commit -m "Initial commit: Online Retail Dashboard"

# Push to GitHub
git branch -M main
git push -u origin main
```

---

## Step 6 — Verify on GitHub

