## After Pushing — Deploy Live (Optional but Recommended)

1. Go to [share.streamlit.io](https://share.streamlit.io)
2. Sign in with your GitHub account
3. Click **New app**
4. Select your repo → branch: `main` → main file: `app.py`
5. Click **Deploy**
6. You get a live URL like `rcrahul-retail.streamlit.app`
7. Add that link to your README and LinkedIn post

